law.text:
Subject to the hearing provisions of § 14-409 of this subtitle, the Department may deny a certificate to any applicant, or suspend or revoke a certificate, if the applicant or certificate holder:
Fraudulently or deceptively obtains or attempts to obtain a certificate for the applicant or certificate holder or for another;
Fraudulently or deceptively uses a certificate;
Violates this subtitle; or
Violates any regulation adopted by the Department under this subtitle.
